&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years of leadership experience in a client-facing roles role within the Automotive sector, preferably in SaaS or digital marketing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated proficiency in understanding digital campaigns, metrics, and analytics&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be operational-minded to identify efficiencies, improve processes, implement strategies, and conduct training sessions to facilitate the ongoing growth of the Customer Success team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to multitask and manage multiple projects and tasks with a strong focus on client satisfaction&lt;/li&gt;
